file.name: health.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Health
  description: Fetch health information about a service instance
  version: 0.1.0
paths:
  /info:
    get:
      summary: Returns health information for the service instance
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Health
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                    alive:
                        type: boolean
                        description: is the service instance healthy
